    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tower defense game with a city-building element!  Voices, alien attributes, and attack patterns are all varied and randomized each game so that each experience is a unique one!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operating from behind your radar screen, in this monochromatic display, you'll direct the special ops units to construct towers in the locations you choose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/e57794da332334a3e56834a6844ff297.poster.avif?t=1764787514\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/e57794da332334a3e56834a6844ff297.webm?t=1764787514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/e57794da332334a3e56834a6844ff297.mp4?t=1764787514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep an eye on your power, support, and supply, as every new build will use and require your available resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/4e5b6b09e8ba474947067870cadbc8db.poster.avif?t=1764787514\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/4e5b6b09e8ba474947067870cadbc8db.webm?t=1764787514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/4e5b6b09e8ba474947067870cadbc8db.mp4?t=1764787514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you run short of supplies, power, or support, you'll need to construct (anywhere you'd like) additional  structures to the base you are trying to defend from alien invaders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/35093c782583a64eedac6275b168acc3.poster.avif?t=1764787514\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/35093c782583a64eedac6275b168acc3.webm?t=1764787514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/35093c782583a64eedac6275b168acc3.mp4?t=1764787514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In a game driven by audio over visuals, you'll get check-ins and updates from your facilities and units, make decisions on how best to build up a basic defense, and learn more about the attackers to improve defensive capabilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/66c56de4e6f177feaeaf8e7f65f1bcff.poster.avif?t=1764787514\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/66c56de4e6f177feaeaf8e7f65f1bcff.webm?t=1764787514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/66c56de4e6f177feaeaf8e7f65f1bcff.mp4?t=1764787514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
